text: Sometimes there is no clarity in voice on other side of phone call while making phone calls to India using phone India calling card .Sometimes there is background noise while making phone call to India using phone India calling card. Sometimes calls can not be completed for some reason when I call to India using phone India calling card as I hear some one saying authentication failed. Please improve your service.
